text: Vasile Hanuseac (born 3 April 1970) is a Romanian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
